            "id": 6325179,
            "title": "盤中速報 - AT&T(T-US)大漲5.07%，報24.17美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>AT&amp;T(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:T:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/T\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">T-US</a>)截至台北時間29日00:21股價上漲1.17美元，報24.17美元，漲幅5.07%，成交量33,648,185（股），盤中最高價24.17美元、最低價23.36美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.02%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.73%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>AT&amp;T(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:T:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/T\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">T-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：0%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.87%</li> <li>近 3 月：-8.15%</li> <li>近 6 月：-16.25%</li> <li>今年以來：-5.6%</li></ul></section></main>",
